{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:"}],"title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(im)removePack:withCompletionHandler:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removePack:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","text":"MLNOfflinePack","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"pack"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"withCompletionHandler:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","preciseIdentifier":"c:MLNOfflineStorage.h@T@MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The offline pack to remove."}]}],"name":"pack"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The completion handler to call once the pack has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"removed. This handler is executed asynchronously on the main queue."}]}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As soon as this method is called on a pack, the pack becomes invalid; any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attempt to send it a message will result in an exception being thrown. If an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"error occurs and the pack cannot be removed, do not attempt to reuse the pack"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object. Instead, if you need continued access to the pack, suspend all packs"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and use the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" method to obtain valid pointers to all the packs."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To detect when any call to this method results in a pack being removed, observe"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"KVO change notifications on the shared offline storage object’s "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" key"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path. Removals from that array result in an "},{"code":"NSKeyValueChangeRemoval","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" change."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When you remove an offline pack, any resources that are required by that pack,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but not other packs, become eligible for deletion from offline storage. Because"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the backing store used for offline storage is also used as a general purpose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cache for map resources, such resources may not be immediately removed if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"implementation determines that they remain useful for general performance of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/removePack:withCompletionHandler:":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:","title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackremovalcompletionhandler","title":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A block to be called once an offline pack has been completely invalidated and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/reloadPacks":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reloadPacks","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/reloadpacks","title":"reloadPacks","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Forcibly, asynchronously reloads the "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property. At some point after this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is called, the pointer values of the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property change, even if the underlying data for these packs has not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changed. If this method is called while a pack is actively downloading, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"behavior is undefined."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","title":"MLNOfflinePack","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]}}}